{"tid":1617354,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"緊急法根本叫「獨裁法」，佢可以隨時要你坐強制性終身監禁！","createTime":"2019-10-03T17:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T07:23:34.000Z","uid":1806,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"2c249a7cc45020a1e200c027b86433afd9811699","tid":1617354,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:56:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kik4UpY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKik4UpY.jpg&h=f6dd3ede&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uYEhuYE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuYEhuYE.jpg&h=5856968c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n只要佢合乎公眾利益規則 <br />\n咁即係林鄭想做咩都得啦<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">送中條例、國歌法、辱警罪等等即刻過晒</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲有</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>在不損害第2條所授予的權力的原則下，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">根據本條例訂立的規例可就任何罪行(不論該罪行屬違反該等規例的罪行或屬任何適用於香港的法律所訂的罪行)，<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>規定以任何刑罰及制裁(包括強制性終身監禁的最高刑罰</ins></span></span></strong>，但不包括死刑)作為該罪行的懲罰 （文宣圖在頭reply上載）</blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔係一般有假釋既終身監禁，係<span style=\"color: orange;\">強制性終身監禁</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外國既緊急法會唔會係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本就係一條徹底既<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">獨裁法</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n因為依個政府已無人性同底線。最worse，如果佢一野set晒暴動罪，非法集結罪等等去到最高刑罰強制性終身監禁，所有反抗既香港人全部終生封印。如此荒謬邪惡既法例，邊個可以接受到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFACEBOOK: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKGETV/posts/134892717849339\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=htt